enum.name: CatAsmAutoSwitchToDesignMode
enum.abstract: Option managing the implicit switch from visualization mode to design mode.

enum.name: CatAsmExtendMoveToFixT
enum.abstract: Option managing the extension of a move to the components involved in a FixTogether.

class.name: AsmConstraintSettingAtt
class.abstract: Represents the Assembly Constraints setting controller object.

method.name: GetConstraintCreationModeInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves informations about the constraint creation setting parameter.

method.name: GetPasteComponentModeInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves informations about the component paste setting parameter.

method.name: GetQuickConstraintModeInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves informations about the quick constraint setting parameter.

method.name: GetQuickConstraintOrderedList
method.abstract: Returns the quick constraint ordered list setting parameter.

method.name: SetConstraintCreationModeLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the constraint creation setting parameter.

method.name: SetPasteComponentModeLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the component paste setting parameter.

method.name: SetQuickConstraintModeLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the quick constraint setting parameter.

method.name: SetQuickConstraintOrderedList
method.abstract: Sets the quick constraint ordered list setting parameter.

method.name: ConstraintCreationMode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the constraint creation setting parameter.

method.name: PasteComponentMode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the component paste setting parameter.

method.name: QuickConstraintMode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the quick constraint setting parameter.

method.name: RedundancyMode
method.abstract: Sets redundancy check option for constraint creation.

class.name: AsmGeneralSettingAtt
class.abstract: Represents the Assembly General setting controller object.

method.name: GetAutoSwitchToDesignModeInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves the state of the implicit switch from visualization mode to design mode setting parameter.

method.name: GetAutoUpdateModeInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves informations about the automatic update setting parameter.

method.name: GetMoveWithFixTExtendModeInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves the state of the setting parameter managing the extension of a move to the components involved in a FixTogether.

method.name: GetUpdateStatusModeInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves informations about the update status computation setting parameter.

method.name: SetAutoSwitchToDesignModeLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the implicit switch from visualization mode to design mode setting parameter.

method.name: SetAutoUpdateModeLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the automatic update setting parameter.

method.name: SetMoveWithFixTExtendModeLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the setting parameter managing the extension of a move to the components involved in a FixTogether.

method.name: SetUpdateStatusModeLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the update status computation setting parameter.

method.name: AutoSwitchToDesignMode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the implicit switch from visualization mode to design mode setting parameter .

method.name: AutoUpdateMode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the automatic update setting parameter.

method.name: MoveWithFixTExtendMode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the setting parameter managing the extension of a move to the components involved in a FixTogether.

method.name: UpdateStatusMode

method.name: Body
method.abstract: Returns the operating body.

method.name: BodyComponent
method.abstract: Returns the component containing the operating body.

method.name: AddAffectedComponent
method.abstract: Adds a component to the affected component list.

method.name: AffectedComponentsCount
method.abstract: Returns the affected component list count.

method.name: ListAffectedComponents
method.abstract: Retrieves the affected component list.

method.name: RemoveAffectedComponent
method.abstract: Removes a component from the affected component list.

class.name: AssemblyFeatures
class.abstract: A collection of all the AssemblyFeature objects of a product.

method.name: AddAssemblyAdd
method.abstract: Creates a new AssemblyBoolean object by adding a body to the assembly.

method.name: AddAssemblyHole
method.abstract: Creates a new AssemblyHole object.

method.name: AddAssemblyPocket
method.abstract: Creates a new AssemblyPocket object.

method.name: AddAssemblyRemove
method.abstract: Creates a new AssemblyBoolean object by removing a body from the assembly.

method.name: AddAssemblySplit
method.abstract: Creates a new AssemblySplit object.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns an AssemblyFeature object using its index or its name from the AssemblyFeatures collection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes an AssemblyFeature object from the AssemblyFeatures collection.

method.name: GetDirection
method.abstract: Retrieves the hole direction vector components.

method.name: GetOrigin
method.abstract: Retrieves the origin point to which the hole is anchored.

method.name: SetDirection
method.abstract: Sets the hole axis direction.

method.name: AnchorMode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the hole anchor mode.

method.name: BottomAngle
method.abstract: Returns the hole bottom angle.

method.name: BottomLimit
method.abstract: Returns the hole bottom limit.

method.name: BottomType
method.abstract: Returns or sets the hole bottom type.

method.name: Diameter

method.name: HeadAngle

method.name: HeadDepth

method.name: HeadDiameter

method.name: Sketch
method.abstract: Returns the hole positioning sketch.

method.name: SketchComponent

method.name: Type
method.abstract: Returns or sets the hole type.

method.name: GetDirection

method.name: FirstLimit

method.name: SecondLimit

method.abstract: Returns the component containing the pocket sketch.
